## Session Start

```javascript
session = load_session_state({
  project_id: "{{PROJECT_ID}}",
  strategy: "relevant",
  include_plan_context: true
})
// Response includes: working_memory, context_snapshot, current_plan_id,
// plan_ascii (rendered wave diagram), project_map, current_git (live snapshot).
// Compare current_git vs context_snapshot.git_snapshot to detect drift.

// Search before creating new tasks
existing = search_tasks({project_id: "{{PROJECT_ID}}", query: "relevant keywords"})

// Tell the user what you found
"Resuming from [date]: [what was happening]
Current work: [task/plan status]
Ready to continue."
```

