## Tags & Phase Labels

Use task tags to mark logical phases of a multi-phase plan:

```javascript
save_task({plan_id: "plan-x", title: "Renderer", tags: ["3a"]})
save_task({plan_id: "plan-x", title: "Migration", tags: ["3b"]})

search_tasks({project_id: "{{PROJECT_ID}}", query: "tag:3a"})
```

Tags compose: `["3a", "frontend"]` is a frontend task in phase 3a. Stay terse.

