## Document Types

`plan_details` | `implementation` | `retrospective` | `guide` | `architecture` | `decision` | `test_report` | `audit` | `security_review` | `observation` | `general` | `offtopic`

`audit` is broad-scope (any review of an area / system); `security_review` is the vuln/threat-model specialization. `observation` captures noticed-but-deferred items first-class. Use `test_report` only for actual test runs.

`save_document` and `update_document` accept `content_file` (absolute path) instead of inline content. `content_file` wins when both are provided.

